reviewText: love the serious and the extra material at the end of each episode.

I thought this was for Christ like people and made from Christ like folks. One of the episodes had men acting like girls and one guy had his wrist slanted, in a gay manner, and asked the other guy did the dress make him look fat?! What?! Not the type of things I want introduced to my kids!
Absolutely exceeded expectations !!! Best kids and family series!! I highly recommend these DVDs . God bless friends and heroes team !
